    "description": {
      "content": "The U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission Recalls Retrieval Web Service is a public, unauthenticated REST API that returns recall records published on cpsc.gov. The endpoint supports XML and JSON output and case-insensitive wildcard search across recall fields such as recall number, company, product type, hazard, country, and UPC.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: U.S. Consumer Product Safety Commission",
